# cppcheck suppressions for the CI static-analysis job (see esphome-ci.yml).
# One suppression per line. Forms:
#   <id>                         suppress everywhere
#   <id>:components/foo/bar.cpp  suppress in one file
#   <id>:components/foo/bar.cpp:42  suppress at one line
# Prefer inline `// cppcheck-suppress <id>` at the call site for one-off cases;
# use this file for whole-file or project-wide false positives.
#
# Keep this list small and justified. If you find yourself suppressing a real
# category wholesale, fix the code or narrow the check set instead.

# Header resolution is intentionally not provided (no compile DB) -- already
# passed as --suppress flags too, listed here for documentation.
missingInclude
missingIncludeSystem
